    <title>E-Tree Support with 2VLAN in E-VPN</title>
    <seriesInfo name="Internet-Draft" value="draft-jiang-l2vpn-evpn-etree-2vlan-00"/>
    <author initials="Y." surname="Jiang" fullname="Yuanlong Jiang">
      <organization>Huawei</organization>
    </author>
    <date day="21" month="September" year="2012"/>
    <abstract>
      <t>   This document discusses how the Dual-VLAN approach as described in
   [Etree-vlan] can be used to support the transport of E-Tree service
   in E-VPN. Thus a single convergent solution is possible for both VPLS
   and E-VPN.

	 </t>
